## 📈 Performance Guidelines

### Query Targets
- Response time: < 500ms (P95)
- Database query: < 200ms (P95)
- Memory: < 100MB per query
- CPU: < 50% sustained

### Optimization Priority
1. Add indexes (5-100x speedup)
2. Fix N+1 queries (10-100x speedup)
3. Use .lean() for reads (15-20% speedup)
4. Add pagination (reduce memory)
5. Aggregate complex queries (varies)

