## 📝 Database Rules

### Indexes
- All `unique: true` fields MUST have indexes
- All frequently queried fields should have indexes
- Compound indexes for common multi-field queries

### Queries
- Use `.lean()` for all read-only queries
- Use `.select()` to exclude unused fields
- Use `.populate()` instead of loops
- Use aggregation for complex queries

### Transactions
- Keep transactions SHORT (not long-running)
- Always use `session.abortTransaction()` in catch
- Don't do external API calls inside transaction

